cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on improving the performance of variational autoencoder (VAE) in generating realistic and natural images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The paper also proposes a multi-view feature extraction strategy, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
